   1051  f4e4							;   Each entry strobes RESM0; the $1C (NOP abs) swallows the next
   1052  f4e4							;   entry's `sta RESM0`, so only the jumped-to strobe executes, then
   1053  f4e4							;   execution falls through to `sta HMOVE` at cycle ~74.
